@item xen_net
A Xen hypervisor virtual network.
@item kvm_net
A KVM hypervisor virtual network
@item esx_net
An ESX/VMWare hypervisor virtual network.
@item test_net
The test hypervisor virtual network.
@item zone
A Solaris zone (future development)
@item ec2
