@item @b{context}: A regular expression to filter on contexts active at host.
@end itemize

@end itemize

Example of a typical body from a context response:

@verbatim
[
  {
    "hostkey": "SHA=33736d45041e2a9407be8cf449aeffa95114bef661c20deaca1bbcfbc2922856",
